WEBVTT

00:00.090 --> 00:01.689
<i>Previously on</i> Sanctuary...

00:01.762 --> 00:03.162
[Druitt]:
We were a part of something,

00:03.192 --> 00:04.658
something we called "the five,"

00:04.660 --> 00:06.026
a small group dedicated

00:06.028 --> 00:07.261
to expanding our knowledge
of the physical world.

00:07.478 --> 00:09.044
Helen was able to procure

00:09.046 --> 00:12.714
a very rare sample of ancient
untainted vampire blood.

00:12.716 --> 00:14.965
After each of us was injected,

00:14.967 --> 00:18.081
we received
unique gifts as a result.

00:18.083 --> 00:19.781
Griffin's molecules
became photosensitive.

00:19.783 --> 00:22.113
Watson's mind
grew to new heights,

00:22.115 --> 00:24.781
and Tesla's reaction
was the most dramatic.

00:24.783 --> 00:28.414
But Helen... her gift was
the most simple. And elegant.

00:28.416 --> 00:31.387
I'm 159 years old.
You have known me for three.

00:31.389 --> 00:32.392
It's an autotype,

00:32.394 --> 00:33.663
one of only five

00:33.665 --> 00:35.932
that were built
during the Second World War.

00:35.934 --> 00:37.802
Without it, the war could have
ended very differently.

